<div style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 25px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 16px; color: #1e293b;">
  <h2 style="color: #d97706; border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0; padding-bottom: 12px; margin-top: 0; font-weight: 900; tracking-tight: -0.5px;">Solicitud de Reserva</h2>
  <p>Hola <strong><%= @client.name %></strong>,</p>
  <p>Se ha generado una solicitud de reserva para la propiedad <strong><%= @property.name %></strong>. Para asegurar tu lugar, por favor confirma tu asistencia:</p>
  <div style="background-color: #fffbeb; border: 1px solid #fef3c7; padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; margin: 20px 0; font-size: 14px;">
    <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0;"><strong>Propiedad:</strong> <span style="color: #0f172a; font-weight: bold;"><%= @property.name %></span></p>
    <% if @property.per_day? %>
      <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0;"><strong>Desde:</strong> <%= l(@reservation.start_time.to_date, format: :long) %></p>
      <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0;"><strong>Hasta:</strong> <%= l((@reservation.end_time - 1.day).to_date, format: :long) %></p>
    <% else %>
      <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0;"><strong>Desde:</strong> <%= l(@reservation.start_time, format: :long) %> hrs</p>
      <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0;"><strong>Hasta:</strong> <%= l(@reservation.end_time, format: :long) %> hrs</p>
    <% end %>
    <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0;"><strong>Código de Reserva:</strong> <code style="background-color: #f1f5f9; color: #4f46e5; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 6px; font-family: monospace; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 0.5px;"><%= @reservation.token %></code></p>
    <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0;"><strong>Estado de Reserva:</strong> <span style="background-color: #fef3c7; color: #92400e; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 10px; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; border: 1px solid #fde68a; display: inline-block;">PENDIENTE DE CONFIRMACIÓN</span></p>
    <% unless @created_by_public %>
      <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Responsable:</strong> <span style="color: #0f172a; font-weight: bold;"><%= @user.first_name %> <%= @user.last_name %></span></p>
    <% end %>
  </div>
  <p style="color: #e11d48; font-size: 13px; text-align: center; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    ⚠️ Este enlace expirará en 24 horas por motivos de seguridad.
  </p>
  <div style="text-align: center; margin: 35px 0; background-color: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 16px; padding: 25px;">
    <div style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
      <a href="<%= confirm_public_reservation_url(@reservation.token) %>" 
         style="background-color: #059669; color: white; padding: 12px 26px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 12px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; display: inline-block; box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.2); margin-right: 10px;">
        Confirmar Reserva
      </a>
      <a href="<%= reject_public_reservation_url(@reservation.token) %>" 
         style="background-color: #e11d48; color: white; padding: 12px 26px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 12px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; display: inline-block; box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(225, 29, 72, 0.2);">
        Rechazar
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p style="font-size: 11px; color: #94a3b8; margin-top: 30px; border-top: 1px solid #f1f5f9; padding-top: 15px; text-align: center; font-style: italic;">
    Si no realizaste esta solicitud, puedes ignorar este correo o rechazar la reserva.
  </p>
  <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 13px; color: #64748b; text-align: center;">
    Atentamente,<br>
    <strong>El equipo de <%= @property.company&.name || "Agenda Pro" %></strong>
  </p>
</div>
